          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What are TD Special Offer GICs?\nPotentially earn a higher rate than traditional GICs while maintaining all the safety and security you expect. These GICs feature attractive interest rates but are available for a limited time. They are offered in a variety of terms to maturity and account types (non-registered, registered, RSP, RESP , RIF and TFSA).\nFor your convenience, TD Special Offer GICs renew automatically at the end of the term into a Guaranteed Investment Certificate whose features are determined at the time of your initial investment so that you don't miss a day of interest.",
